      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Dynasty_Rank.png">2f7d0004:00000000:5e33eac6fd62be53</T>
      <T n="text">0x3AE61421<!--String: "Dynasty Ranking is the position of a Sim within their Dynasty, dependent on the amount of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Prestige</font></b> they have contributed by adhering to the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dynasty Values</font></b>. Having a higher rank can reward them with positive moodlets and social advantages when interacting with other members, whereas a lower rank may make them more likely to be declared an <b><font color='#199C2C'>Outcast</font></b>.\n\nIf a Sim reaches a Rank that's higher than the Dynasty Head, they are considered to be a more prolific member of the Dynasty and can <b><font color='#199C2C'>usurp the Headship</font></b> to reflect their status."--></T>
    </U>
